---

## 6. **Backend API Endpoints (Node.js Example)**

```js
// POST /api/auth/signup
{ role: "creator", email: "...", password: "...", name: "..." }

// POST /api/tracks/upload (Creator only)
{ file: MP3, title, artist, genre, coverArt, isrc }

// GET /api/me/analytics (Creator)
→ { streams: 12040, earnings: 36.12, topCountries: [...] }

// GET /api/search?q=afrobeat
→ { tracks: [...], artists: [...] }
```

---

## 7. **Monetization & Legal**

- **Revenue Model:**
  - **Freemium**: Ads (Google AdSense) for free users
  - **Premium**: $4.99/mo (no ads, offline, HD audio)
  - **Creator Cut**: 80% of net revenue (after platform fees)

- **Legal Must-Haves:**
  - DMCA compliance
  - Music licensing (work with PROs like ASCAP, BMI, or indie distributors)
  - Age verification (COPPA)
  - GDPR/CCPA privacy policy

